snippet.title: Dune PC Intro (CD)
snippet.description:
The CD-Rom intro of the 1992 adventure/real-time-strategy game Dune, believed by many to be the most immersive Dune game created.
visually stunning and unique, Dune could be one of the best games of the last century.
